reviewText: This flick kept me glued to the screen from the opening scene.  The acting and cinematography were first rate!  If you like horror, you won't want to miss this one!

Our Kingdom Come is a great b-horror film right out of Boston, MA! It's creepy, funny, and action-packed. The characters are interesting and unique as is the plot- something that does not always accompany b-horror films. I say check it out without a doubt!
